AGI - The Polaria police deposited in the offices of the Civitavecchia Prosecutor the information in which the episode of the theft of a perfume box by the speaker Piero Fassino> in a duty-free shop of Fiumicino and cost a complaint. Attached to the enclosure also the video of what happened on April 15 last in the port of call of the Capital.
&nbsp;
In recent days it has emerged that from the account of some employees of the shop Fassino would have been author of an attempt to theft. According to Corriere della Sera, similar versions provided by six witnesses speak of "three episodes in one month". It will now be up to the pm to decide how to proceed and whether to entrust delegations to the judicial police to carry out further in depth.

